This is just a inital installation to prepare the enviroment for use
installing the graisl 1.3.7 and grails2 || mysql5.1 || and java

to successfully complete your installation
you need to give chmod +x initial_installation.sh
run file with ./initial_installation.sh

after all instalations 
you need to edit bashrc 
	example: vi /home/user/.bashrc
and add the editbashrc content into the bashrc file

bye
